Fix: Correcting anchor element

When change from Link to anchor, forgot to include a dynamic href which caused the landing page to include the user key

Refactor: Improved Naming and Cleanup

Improved naming to encodeUser, cleanup comments in the login and signup files ; Improved typing in components utilising interfaces better

Fix: Incorrect interface

Optional in opt props meant possibly undefined

Fix: Incorrect interface

Interface allowed the setOpen hook to return bool, but it returns void

Feat: menu close on click

Menu would remain open after option was clicked requiring manual closure after page change
